_sText:
This map is a port from CSGO. The map was created by thorgot the creator of jb_avalanche and jb_airship 2 great maps which are in counter strike source already ;). This map is based on Undertale, a game by Toby Fox.

In this port, I had to take out/replace a few minigames and secrets due to limitations in hammer compared to CSGO.

Still, this map comes with a great list of features which include :

Minigames in cells
Decathlon  
Strafe Jump: easy, medium, and hard; 0, 5, or 10 damage 
Slide Race: 4 different courses
Dodge Course: Dodge obstacles on a moving platform 
Surf: easy, medium, and hard; 0, 5, or 10 damage; recall and gate buttons 
Risky Ralph's Roulette (the CT pressing the button also has a chance of dying) 
Extreme Jumprope (Jumprope combined with 4 colors) 
9 Colors with 4 brand new events (19 total) 
Soccer
Spleef 
Easy Climb, Medium Climb, and Hard Climb 
Disco (with Undertale music) 
25 key piano that can be played. 
Secrets and vents.

An sG community map created by thorgot.
Additional textures and brushwork by Prussia.
Music remixes/covers by RichaadEB, ToxicxEternity, and theultimateonejpsx.
Models by Humin, RED_EYE, Brewster T. Koopa, and Yok99102.
Ported to Counter-Strike Source by Fronexe.
